<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='806629' id='t-806629'>What lies within us can
never be truly colonized,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='809346' id='t-809346'>contorted, or taken away.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='811702' id='t-811702'>The light never goes out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='815800' id='t-815800'>As a very wonderful
doctor once said to me,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817910' id='t-817910'>&quot;Don't tell me what other people
have told you about yourself.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821161' id='t-821161'>Tell me about you.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='824212' id='t-824212'>Thank you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='826018' id='t-826018'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
